# Environment variables

Copy to `.env` (local) and set in Vercel project settings.

## Public site + admin (required for dynamic images)

```
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_KEY
```

If these are missing, the app falls back to scanning `public/assets/hotels/` at build time (legacy).

## Optional: migration script only

Do **not** expose the service role in the browser. Use only in `scripts/migrate-local-to-supabase.mjs` via a local file such as `.env.migrate` (gitignored).

```
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key
```
